</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,797,291,316]" box="[151,797,291,316]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<bibRefCitation author="Downey, M. E." box="[151,335,291,316]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="1 - 57" refId="ref46093" refString="Downey, M. E. (1986) Revision of the Atlantic Brisingida (Echinodermata: Asteroidea), with description of a new genus and family. Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology, 435, 1 - 57." type="journal article" year="1986">Downey 1986: 36</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Clark, A. M. &amp; Downey, M. E." box="[346,632,292,316]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" refId="ref45928" refString="Clark, A. M. &amp; Downey, M. E. (1992) Starfishes of the Atlantic. Chapman and Hall, London, 794 pp." type="book" year="1992">Clark &amp; Downey 1992: 479</bibRefCitation>
; Mah 1996: 273
</paragraph>
